title: Flight Simulator 2020 - How to - Cessna 208 B Gran Caravan - Set flight plan manually
description:
In this how to we are going to look how we can configure our flight plan manually in our navigation system from our Cessna 208 B Gran Caravan. 

Route being configure will be from John Lennon/Liverpool Airport
(EGGP) to Prestwick Airport (EGPK).
